trans-unit.source: Exposes <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"></xref> control types to [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Przedstawia <xref href="System.Windows.Automation.ControlType.Document"> </xref> kontrolować typów do [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The DocumentAutomationPeer represents documents and supports the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.
trans-unit.target: DocumentAutomationPeer reprezentuje dokumentów i obsługuje <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: Objects such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> can contain embedded objects, such as images and hyperlinks.
trans-unit.target: Obiekty, takie jak <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>lub <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>mogą zawierać osadzonych obiektów, takich jak obrazy i hiperłącza.</xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument>

trans-unit.source: Initially, when you try to get the child elements of the document, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> does not return the embedded objects.
trans-unit.target: Początkowo podczas próby pobrania podrzędnych elementów dokumentu, <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>nie może zwracać obiekty osadzone.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To get the embedded elements, obtain a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> from the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> and call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Aby uzyskać osadzone elementy, uzyskać <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>i Wywołaj <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>

trans-unit.source: After <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName> is called, any elements in that <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> are returned by <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Po <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>jest nazywany żadnego z elementów w tym <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>są zwracane przez <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.DocumentAutomationPeer.GetChildrenCore%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Unless you know the document is a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, you should not call <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Znając dokumentu jest <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>, nie należy wywołać <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>na <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Właściwości.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern.DocumentRange%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>

trans-unit.source: If the document is loaded from a network location, calling <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A> on the entire document is resource intensive.
trans-unit.target: Jeśli dokument został załadowany z lokalizacji sieciowej, wywoływania <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>w całym dokumencie jest zasobem znacznym.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange.GetChildren%2A>

trans-unit.source: Instead, you should use one of the methods on <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern> that returns a <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> that represents a portion of the document.
trans-unit.target: Zamiast niej, powinny używać jednej z metod na <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>zwracającą <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange>reprezentujący części dokumentu.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.Text.TextPatternRange> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.TextPattern>

trans-unit.source: This property does not indicate whether the element is visible.
trans-unit.target: Ta właściwość wskazuje, czy element jest widoczny.

trans-unit.source: In some circumstances, an element is on the screen but is still not visible.
trans-unit.target: W niektórych sytuacjach element znajduje się na ekranie, ale jest nadal niewidoczny.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the element is obscured by other elements, it might not be visible.
trans-unit.target: Na przykład jeśli element jest zasłonięty przez inne elementy, jego może nie być widoczna.

trans-unit.source: In this case, the method returns `false`.
trans-unit.target: W tym przypadku metoda zwraca `false`.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the element is not on the screen; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Jeśli element nie jest na ekranie; w przeciwnym razie <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
